videos.description: UConn's Sidney Wilson rejects Trey Wade with a vicious swat, then hammers home a put-back dunk on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Wilson elevates for big block, put-back dunk) 2020/01/12

videos.headline: Wilson elevates for big block, put-back dunk

videos.description: UConn's Josh Carlton misses a free throw, but gets his own rebound and throws down a powerful two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carlton follows missed FT with huge slam) 2020/01/12

videos.headline: Carlton follows missed FT with huge slam

videos.description: Wichita State's Trey Wade slams a powerful dunk off the inbound pass.
videos.headline: Wade slams inbounds alley-oop

videos.description: UConn's Sidney Wilson sinks a three-pointer with one second left in regulation to send the game to overtime.
videos.headline: Wilson forces OT with game-tying 3
